<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_e05cac5c-5949-4033-9c11-9f84c68f7340" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>F1D10</sptc><title id="_ee8b1cf5-2147-4977-b93f-31fab683d5fa">Surface finishes</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_12cc640b-a464-4459-a68d-8482c480e06e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_0426b1c7-6269-4c43-a193-aa7157ca6924">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In a building or part of a building, the flooring or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/9503_0.4.0.xml#_f54e63b7-9207-4230-ada9-671324d1dbb6" id="_1d8ab40d-be36-45be-bd2b-f69b10699b69" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">surface finish</xref> of a roof, balcony, terrace, podium, or similar part of a building must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_18185e98-955e-4886-859a-d463d1cd203c"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/9482_0.4.0.xml#_ebe4825e-9ef4-4895-853d-e9d6c464c9e9" id="_328449dc-2f90-4de0-a7c1-18e6568f7dd0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">self-draining</xref>; or</li><li id="_3f36da40-a597-48e4-a5d7-bb0abd511052">directly fixed to a membrane complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4966_0.27.0.xml#_458b78ec-911a-4b5f-8160-057e0892653c" id="_284f8413-f81e-418d-9e06-419d7e2783f2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">F1D7</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_e7552860-3fe1-4444-ad25-e27ff35ccf5b"><callout-type ncc-info-type="limitation"/><p>F1D10(a) does not apply to areas subject to vehicular traffic or limited trafficability stone/pebble coverings (ballast) to roof membranes</p></callout></clause>